        political_note: `Avvaiyar composed this poem in the context of the competitive gift-giving culture of Sangam Tamil Nadu. Kings and chieftains established their status by giving — to poets, to the poor, to allies. Avvaiyar's poems are part of that economy while simultaneously stepping outside it to evaluate it.`
